description: Demolition of existing buildings and development of 3 blocks of between 3 and 7 stories, comprising a total of 283 studio 1, 2, 3 bed flats, ground floor retail/ non-residential institute/ Assembly and Leisure (Class A1 and flexible Class A1 / A2 / A3 / D1 / D2) and commercial (Class B1) units; with vehicle access from adelaide road, servicing, car and cycle parking, refuse storage, landscaping, public and private amenity space and village square open space.
